data.description: LARGE Lot .41 Acres with sparkling pool & large yard! Home features 4 large Bedrooms & 3 Baths. Master suite & guest bedroom is downstairs (along with a second bedroom) with 2 large bedrooms upstairs! Large kitchen opens to family room (or dining room) with slider to a large covered patio with view of the pool, children's play structure & garden - perfect yard for entertaining! Newer dual pane windows throughout! Upgraded ceiling fans. Covered RV parking plus extra parking space in the driveway. Shelves & workbench in the garage. Orange tree, grapevine, & blackberries. Plus your own Chicken Coop! This home has it all! Come bring your personal touches & make it this your own bit of paradise!!
